e="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Executioner understudies&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/08/3</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 08:13:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-08 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/08/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Faba4e860e9ef0137cf93005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Look. If you’re so self-conscious about it, get yourself a gorilla mask.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/08/2</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 08:12:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-08 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/08/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fee48055b58c311ea8bf6005056a9" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Another photograph from the Hubble Space Telescope&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/08/1</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 08:11:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-08 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/08/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F12df3670fa880137d531005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Well, here he comes … Mr. Never-Makes-a-Dud.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/08/0</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 08:10:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-07 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fd811ca10e92e0137cf47005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;The Viking longcar was once the scourge of European roadways.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/4</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 08:09:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-07 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fe6eb2820cdd30137c56b005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/3</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 08:08:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-07 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F709c15c0e92d0137cf47005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“New guy, huh? Well, up here, you walk the edge! And the edge is a fickle hellcat. … Love her, but never trust her, for her heart is full of lye! ”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/2</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 08:07:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-07 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fad1dd400d0ea0137c64d005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“This is it, Jenkins—indisputable proof that the Ice Age caught these people completely off guard.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/1</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 08:06:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-07 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F3d725c709ee701396086005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Okay, okay, little Ahab. … Which one is it going to be?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/07/0</guid><pubDate>Tue, 07 Apr 2026 08:05:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-06 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F11e86bd0d8ba0137c959005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“CANNONBAAAAAAAALLLLLLLLL!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/4</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 08:04:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-06 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/3</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F3ec4874002810138d7bb005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Anatidaephobia: the fear that somewhere, somehow, a duck is watching you.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/3</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 08:03:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-06 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/2</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F74e5b2b0e3ae0137cd49005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Darren’s heart quickened: Once inside the home, and once the demonstration was in full swing, a sale was inevitable.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/2</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 08:02:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-06 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/1</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Ff2d4ca50027e0138d7ba005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Can I look now?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/1</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 08:01:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-04-06 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F36507e20e9ee0137cf93005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;And for the rest of his life, Ernie told his friends that he had talked with God.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/04/06/0</guid><pubDate>Mon, 06 Apr 2026 08:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>